## Completeness Checklist

- [ ] Clarification ID assigned and unique within the log
- [ ] Question is specific and answerable
- [ ] Context explains why the clarification is needed
- [ ] Owner is the person responsible for chasing the answer
- [ ] Deadline is set and agreed with the project manager
- [ ] Impact if unresolved is documented
- [ ] Status reflects current state
- [ ] If resolved/escalated/waived: resolution record completed
- [ ] If resolved: decision reference linked
